<td>An optional string describing the host designated by the URL. [<cite><a=
 class=3D"bibref" data-link-type=3D"biblio" href=3D"https://spec.openapis.o=
rg/oas/v3.0.3.html#bib-commonmark" title=3D"CommonMark Spec">CommonMark</a>=
</cite>] syntax <em class=3D"rfc2119">MAY</em> be used for rich text repres=
entation.</td>
