<td><span id=3D"serverVariables"></span>variables</td>
<td style=3D"text-align:center">Map[<code>string</code>, <a href=3D"https:/=
/spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.3.html#server-variable-object">Server Variable =
Object</a>]</td>
<td>A map between a variable name and its value.  The value is used for sub=
stitution in the server=E2=80=99s URL template.</td>
