<td><strong><em class=3D"rfc2119">REQUIRED</em></strong>. The default value=
 to use for substitution, which <em class=3D"rfc2119">SHALL</em> be sent if=
 an alternate value is <em>not</em> supplied. Note this behavior is differe=
