s://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.3.html#path-templating-matching" aria-label=
=3D"Permalink for Section 4.7.8.2"></a></div>
<p>Assuming the following paths, the concrete definition, <code>/pets/mine<=
/code>, will be matched first if used:</p>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code>  /pets/{petId}
  /pets/mine
</code></pre>
<p>The following paths are considered identical and invalid:</p>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code>  /pets/{petId}
  /pets/{name}
</code></pre>
<p>The following may lead to ambiguous resolution:</p>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code>  /{entity}/me
  /books/{id}
</code></pre>
