>Path Item Object</h4><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://spec.openapis.=
org/oas/v3.0.3.html#path-item-object" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 4=
.7.9"></a></div>
<p>Describes the operations available on a single path.
A Path Item <em class=3D"rfc2119">MAY</em> be empty, due to <a href=3D"http=
s://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.3.html#security-filtering">ACL constraints</=
a>.
The path itself is still exposed to the documentation viewer but they will =
not know which operations and parameters are available.</p>
