<tr>
<td><span id=3D"callbackExpression"></span>{expression}</td>
<td style=3D"text-align:center"><a href=3D"https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3=
.0.3.html#path-item-object">Path Item Object</a></td>
<td>A Path Item Object used to define a callback request and expected respo=
nses.  A <a href=3D"https://learn.openapis.org/examples/v3.0/callback-examp=
le.html">complete example</a> is available.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
