ype</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">Cat:</span>  <span class=3D"hljs-comment">## =
"Cat" will be used as the discriminator value</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">description:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-str=
ing">A</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">representation</span> <span class=
