</section><section id=3D"xml-arrays"><div class=3D"header-wrapper"><h6 id=
=3D"x4-7-26-2-4-xml-arrays"><bdi class=3D"secno">4.7.26.2.4 </bdi>XML Array=
s</h6><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.3.h=
tml#xml-arrays" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 4.7.26.2.4"></a></div>
<p>Changing the element names:</p>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code><span class=3D"hljs-punctua=
tion">{</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"animals"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation=
">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">{</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"type"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation"=
>:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">"array"</span><span class=3D"hljs-pun=
ctuation">,</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"items"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation=
">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">{</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"type"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuatio=
n">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">"string"</span><span class=3D"hljs-=
punctuation">,</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"xml"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation=
">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">{</span>
        <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"name"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuat=
ion">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">"animal"</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span>
<span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code><span class=3D"hljs-attr">a=
nimals:</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">array<=
/span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-attr">items:</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">stri=
ng</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">xml:</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">an=
imal</span>
</code></pre>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code><span class=3D"hljs-tag">&l=
t;<span class=3D"hljs-name">animal</span>&gt;</span>value<span class=3D"hlj=
s-tag">&lt;/<span class=3D"hljs-name">animal</span>&gt;</span>
<span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;<span class=3D"hljs-name">animal</span>&gt;</s=
pan>value<span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class=3D"hljs-name">animal</sp=
an>&gt;</span>
</code></pre>
<p>The external <code>name</code> property has no effect on the XML:</p>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code><span class=3D"hljs-punctua=
tion">{</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"animals"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation=
">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">{</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"type"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation"=
>:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">"array"</span><span class=3D"hljs-pun=
ctuation">,</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"items"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation=
">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">{</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"type"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuatio=
n">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">"string"</span><span class=3D"hljs-=
punctuation">,</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"xml"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation=
">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">{</span>
        <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"name"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuat=
ion">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">"animal"</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuatio=
n">,</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"xml"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">=
:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">{</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"name"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuatio=
n">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">"aliens"</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span>
<span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code><span class=3D"hljs-attr">a=
nimals:</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">array<=
/span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-attr">items:</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">stri=
ng</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">xml:</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">an=
imal</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-attr">xml:</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">alie=
ns</span>
</code></pre>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code><span class=3D"hljs-tag">&l=
t;<span class=3D"hljs-name">animal</span>&gt;</span>value<span class=3D"hlj=
s-tag">&lt;/<span class=3D"hljs-name">animal</span>&gt;</span>
<span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;<span class=3D"hljs-name">animal</span>&gt;</s=
pan>value<span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class=3D"hljs-name">animal</sp=
an>&gt;</span>
</code></pre>
<p>Even when the array is wrapped, if a name is not explicitly defined, the=
 same name will be used both internally and externally:</p>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code><span class=3D"hljs-punctua=
tion">{</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"animals"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation=
">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">{</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"type"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation"=
>:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">"array"</span><span class=3D"hljs-pun=
ctuation">,</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"items"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation=
">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">{</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"type"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuatio=
n">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">"string"</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuatio=
n">,</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"xml"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">=
:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">{</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"wrapped"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctua=
tion">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-literal"><span class=3D"hljs-keyword">tr=
ue</span></span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span>
<span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code><span class=3D"hljs-attr">a=
nimals:</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">array<=
/span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-attr">items:</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">stri=
ng</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-attr">xml:</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">wrapped:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-literal">=
true</span>
</code></pre>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code><span class=3D"hljs-tag">&l=
t;<span class=3D"hljs-name">animals</span>&gt;</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;<span class=3D"hljs-name">animals</span>&gt;=
</span>value<span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class=3D"hljs-name">animals=
</span>&gt;</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;<span class=3D"hljs-name">animals</span>&gt;=
</span>value<span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class=3D"hljs-name">animals=
</span>&gt;</span>
<span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class=3D"hljs-name">animals</span>&gt;<=
/span>
</code></pre>
<p>To overcome the naming problem in the example above, the following defin=
ition can be used:</p>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code><span class=3D"hljs-punctua=
tion">{</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"animals"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation=
">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">{</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"type"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation"=
>:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">"array"</span><span class=3D"hljs-pun=
ctuation">,</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"items"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation=
">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">{</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"type"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuatio=
n">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">"string"</span><span class=3D"hljs-=
punctuation">,</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"xml"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation=
">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">{</span>
        <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"name"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuat=
ion">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">"animal"</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuatio=
n">,</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"xml"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">=
:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">{</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">"wrapped"</span><span class=3D"hljs-punctua=
tion">:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-literal"><span class=3D"hljs-keyword">tr=
ue</span></span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span>
<span class=3D"hljs-punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code><span class=3D"hljs-attr">a=
nimals:</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">array<=
/span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-attr">items:</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">stri=
ng</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">xml:</span>
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-string">an=
imal</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-attr">xml:</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-attr">wrapped:</span> <span class=3D"hljs-literal">=
true</span>
</code></pre>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code><span class=3D"hljs-tag">&l=
t;<span class=3D"hljs-name">animals</span>&gt;</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;<span class=3D"hljs-name">animal</span>&gt;<=
/span>value<span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class=3D"hljs-name">animal</=
span>&gt;</span>
  <span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;<span class=3D"hljs-name">animal</span>&gt;<=
/span>value<span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class=3D"hljs-name">animal</=
span>&gt;</span>
<span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class=3D"hljs-name">animals</span>&gt;<=
/span>
</code></pre>
<p>Affecting both internal and external names:</p>
<pre class=3D"nohighlight" tabindex=3D"0"><code><span class=3D"hljs-punctua=
